{"tid":1363542,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田區議會連儂牆","createTime":"2019-07-25T08:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T08:20:52.000Z","uid":101510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ccdf1cf1380abf2f29623c1b9250b59f4e97571a","tid":1363542,"uid":101510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"沙田區議會今天兩時半舉行會議，民政處指早上已有大量市民輪候公眾席，公眾席已滿座為由，拒絕更多市民入場及記者進入場地採訪。民主派區議員及後協助市民和傳媒入場。沙田區議會主席何厚祥指會場混亂，宣布休會15分鐘，建制派議員及官員代表離席。<br />\n<br />\n現時 19 名區議員仍留在會議室內，市民亦把memo紙貼在會議室的沙田區議會徽號下，形成一幅「沙田區議會連儂牆」。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片由沙田區議員陳兆陽提供)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O3sppYi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO3sppYi.jpg&h=b2cabeec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b946a59d90ad2a748d30030035eafc120ee35416","tid":1363542,"uid":101510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:07:12.000Z","msg":"沙田友真係好高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6b4177033095cb453cc1543422fbb7bffda381","tid":1363542,"uid":280979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:20:52.000Z","msg":"Help push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1363363/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1363363/page/1</a><br />\n去信聯合國第二波：檢舉黑警人人有責"}]}